if not databank then
    system.print("ERROR: No databank connected!")
    unit.exit()
    return
end

local keys = databank.getKeyList()
system.print("=== DATABANK KEYS (" .. #keys .. " total) ===")

if #keys == 0 then
    system.print("Databank is EMPTY!")
    system.print("You need to run the scanner first.")
else
    -- Group keys by type
    local itemKeys = {}
    local containerListKeys = {}
    local containerDetailKeys = {}
    local otherKeys = {}
    
    for _, key in ipairs(keys) do
        if string.match(key, "^c%.") then
            table.insert(containerDetailKeys, key)
        elseif string.match(key, "%.c$") then
            table.insert(containerListKeys, key)
        elseif string.match(key, "^[a-z]") then
            table.insert(itemKeys, key)
        else
            table.insert(otherKeys, key)
        end
    end
    
    if #itemKeys > 0 then
        system.print("")
        system.print("ITEM KEYS (" .. #itemKeys .. "):")
        for _, key in ipairs(itemKeys) do
            system.print("  " .. key)
        end
    end
    
    if #containerListKeys > 0 then
        system.print("")
        system.print("CONTAINER LIST KEYS (" .. #containerListKeys .. "):")
        for _, key in ipairs(containerListKeys) do
            system.print("  " .. key)
        end
    end
    
    if #containerDetailKeys > 0 then
        system.print("")
        system.print("CONTAINER DETAIL KEYS (" .. #containerDetailKeys .. "):")
        for i = 1, math.min(10, #containerDetailKeys) do
            system.print("  " .. containerDetailKeys[i])
        end
        if #containerDetailKeys > 10 then
            system.print("  ... and " .. (#containerDetailKeys - 10) .. " more")
        end
    end
    
    if #otherKeys > 0 then
        system.print("")
        system.print("OTHER KEYS (" .. #otherKeys .. "):")
        for _, key in ipairs(otherKeys) do
            system.print("  " .. key)
        end
    end
end

unit.exit()
